(3) Certification from the Department of Trade and Industry that the debtor has no registered business, 
(4) Certification from the Securities and Exchange Commission that the Corporation is no longer active, 
(5) Certificate of no residence in the barangay of the municipality/city of last known address, 
(6) Proof of exhaustion of all remedies to collect the receivable and demand to liquidate the cash advances and fund transfers, such as but not limited to copies of served or returned demand letters, 
